data.title: Phyllis Logan and Walter Dumanski - Marriage Records
data.meta_description: Ancestry.ca has at least 1 marriage record for Phyllis Logan and Walter Dumanski, among more than 1271 marriage records for the surname Logan and more than 4 marriage records for the surname Dumanski.
data.text:
Ancestry.ca, the largest online family history resource, can help you explore marriage records for Phyllis Logan and Walter Dumanski from among its billions of historical records from Canada and around the world.

Marriage records are primary resources for the marriage details, since they were created at the time of the marriage. Ancestry.ca collections include indexes that can help you request the record, and in some cases, actual images of the marriage records.
